ğŸ—„ Database Design

The system includes relational tables such as:
	â€¢	patient
	â€¢	diagnosis
	â€¢	treatment
	â€¢	tests
	â€¢	patientvisit

Key design features:
	â€¢	A diagnosis can map to multiple treatments and tests
	â€¢	A patient can have multiple visits
	â€¢	Visits may include tests even without a diagnosis
	â€¢	Foreign key relationships enforce data consistency

The database file (medicalDatabase.db) is automatically generated on first execution.

